<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798c79cfd4b27c319fb2a96e460eb21a3f7a5361","tid":2301541,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"到底有無証據? 無証據隨口講都可以叫專家?"},{"pid":"0c1fe34120c42d4595cfc71d4de67553f56411c9","tid":2301541,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"年年流感都變種, 幾時有人關心過咩源頭? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單嘢係場全球共產陰謀嚟, 幕後策劃係聯合國, 唔係中國共產黨 <br />\n<br />\nDr. Tedros唔係醫生，係埃塞俄比亞共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聯合國係個共產陰謀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8199719/Dr-Tedros-Ghebreyesus-career-politician-running-China-centric-WHO.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8199719%2FDr-Tedros-Ghebreyesus-career-politician-running-China-centric-WHO.html&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=91329d31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8199719/Dr-Tedros-Ghebreyesus-career-politician-running-China-centric-WHO.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, a little-known figure before the coronavirus pandemic, has risen to prominence as Director-General of the World Health Organisation which is spearheading global responses to the virus.<br />\n<br />\nDr Tedros - who has never practised as a medical doctor - is a career politician who was born in what is now Eritrea, began work under the Communist Derg junta, came to study in the UK, then rose to the top of Ethiopia's government first as Health Minister and then Foreign Minister before being elected to lead the WHO in 2017."},{"pid":"1a555fcab469e2038de16ef8b3e18c85c7b8770f","tid":2301541,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:39:25.000Z","msg":"隔咗年幾先去<br />\n所謂調查，係咪好似恩雨之聲「發現」羅亞方舟殘骸咁？<br />\n咁耐恐龍化石都搵唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66320027d2f38942a5dbc5118210dc66508b2a76","tid":2301541,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"當人on9 但又會有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d5e25d714e911bef7c73cde9d8a69d5d8eb61f","tid":2301541,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c8fabb881feea74e67a191ef598d6b6b9a61aa9f","tid":2301541,"uid":24140,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"哂gas<br />\n袁國勇1月果陣上過去啦<br />\n果陣已經話咩都燒哂，sample 同dna資料都無埋<br />\nwho仲去黎做咩？<br />\n<br />\n食野味補身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"搞下幼幼<br />\n大家嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n袋袋平安<br />\n最後源頭出自意粉國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a98f84ce76fe0b1f74b2345081b399ae1ed031b","tid":2301541,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:52:58.000Z","msg":"拜登：<br />\n病毒係來自美國<br />\n請唔好針對中國"},{"pid":"d2b04db21dd81aac9e31e72c58de8a7e2a69b1d6","tid":2301541,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"咁多零號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c7e6afcd3928f962a876731b1a455d0d54afbb","tid":2301541,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BfY6Osq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBfY6Osq.jpg&h=fc1751f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9d6e03072cc8daab2267be4e75a9be31720f85c","tid":2301541,"uid":160122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2da93aba1bf48c05bdc65b79d3686b3733e3c536","tid":2301541,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T